---
description: React frontend folder structure
globs:
  - "frontend/src/**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}"
alwaysApply: false
---
- `frontend/src/api`: API calls.
- `frontend/src/components`: reusable UI components.
- `frontend/src/hooks`: shared React hooks.
- `frontend/src/lib`: utilities and helpers.
- `frontend/src/pages`: page-level views.
- `frontend/src/stores`: shared state.
- `frontend/src/types`: shared types.
- `frontend/src/main.tsx`: app entry.
- `frontend/src/App.tsx`: root component.
